text: And the Lord commanded Jossu with a son of none, and said, Take courage and be valiant, for thou shalt bring the children of Israel into the land which I have promised, and I will be with thee.

segments.text: And the Lord commanded Jossu with a son of none, and said,
Take courage and be valiant, for thou shalt bring the children of Israel into the land which I have promised, and I will be with thee.
